    "game-id": "de06c1450ddf17a0a4a3f4ecf00dbae5",
    "spell_type": "focus",
    "rank": 1,
    "text": "Your body sprouts brambly thorns that thrive on life magic. Adjacent creatures that hit you with a melee attack, as well as creatures that hit you with unarmed attacks, take 1 piercing damage each time they do. Anytime you cast a vitality spell, the thorns' damage increases to 1d6 until the start of your next turn.",
